20helping%20my%20dad%20and%20stepmom%20get%20our%20house%20organized%20to%20host%20her%20mom's%20side%20of%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%204%3A00%20pm%2C%20a%20flurry%20of%20casserole%20dishes%20and%20running%20children%20descend%20on%20our%20house.%20I%20have%20just%20enough%20time%20to%20hug%20everyone%20hello%20%E2%80%94%20plus%20grab%20one%20plateful%20of%20turkey%20%E2%80%94%20before%20I'm%20off%20to%20my%20second%20Christmas%20Eve%20dinner%20with%20my%20mom's%20side%20of%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can%20double%20book%20Christmas%20Eve%20because%20my%20mom's%20family%20runs%20on%20%26quot%3BAng%20Time%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20when%20I%20show%20up%20at%207%3A00%20pm%2C%20there's%20a%20good%20chance%20I'll%20be%20the%20first%20one%20there%20and%20responsible%20for%20decorating%20the%20tree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Angs%20don't%20mind%20starting%20Christmas%20late%20because%20they%20party%20late%20too.%20Our%20tradition%20is%20not%20to%20open%20any%20presents%20until%20midnight%2C%20and%20as%20the%20presents%20usually%20involve%20wine%2C%20I'm%20not%20out%20of%20there%20until%203%3A00%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDec%2025%3A%20Christmas%20Day%20starts%20with%20a%20late%20brunch%20and%20ends%20with%20an%20early%20dinner%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20I'm%20past%20my%20%26quot%3Brace%20downstairs%20to%20see%20what%20Santa%20brought%20me%20at%20the%20crack%20of%20dawn%26quot%3B%20days%2C%20I%20sleep%20in%20with%20just%20enough%20time%20to%20enjoy%20a%20Christmas%20day%20brunch%20with%20my%20mom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20it's%20back%20to%20my%20dad's%20house%20to%20load%20up%20the%20car%20and%20drive%20to%20his%20family's%20hometown%20for%20Christmas%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20stark%20contrast%20to%20the%20Angs%2C%20the%20Canning%20side%20of%20my%20family%20manages%20to%20get%20dinner%2C%20dessert%2C%20a%20Santa%20appearance%2C%20and%20a%20complete%20clean%20up%20done%20by%207%3A00%20pm.%20I'm%20talking%20dishes%20dried%20and%20floors%20