%3Cfigcaption%3ESoftware%20engineer%20Sheldon%20Chi%20(not%20pictured)%20is%20a%20tech%20worker%20who%20helps%20other%20people%20get%20jobs%20in%20tech%20with%20his%20training%20company.%3Cp%3ELuis%20Alvarez%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESheldon%20Chi%C2%A0%20has%20worked%20for%20Amazon%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20two%20tech%20start%20ups.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20says%20there%20are%20important%20things%20to%20consider%20before%20accepting%20a%20job%20at%20any%20tech%20company.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFor%20instance%2C%20employees%20don't%20always%20make%20more%20money%20at%20Big%20Tech%20companies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Sheldon%20Chi%2C%20a%2036-year-old%20software%20engineer%20from%20Canada%20about%20how%20to%20get%20a%20job%20at%20a%20tech%20company.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20began%20my%20career%20in%202016%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%20working%20at%20startups.%20Then%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-at-amazon-jobs-performance-reviews-hiring-firing-interviews-warehouses-delivery-drivers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworked%20at%20Amazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20getting%20a%20job%20at%20Google.%20Today%2C%20I%20run%20my%20own%20company%20where%20I%20train%20tech%20workers%20on%20how%20to%20pass%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Falgo.monster%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoding%20interview%20test%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsystemdesignschool.io%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esystem%20design%20interview%20test%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20a%20job%20at%20any%20tech%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20at%20a%20startup%20is%20very%20different%20from%20working%20at%20a%20Big%20Tech%20company.%20They%20require%20different%20skills%20and%20motivations.%20I%20worked%20at%20two%20different%20startups%20for