manded%20by%20the%20ICC%20for%20it.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FUz_Khawaja%2Fstatus%2F1734830493890404372%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3EKhwaja%20spoke%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20defended%20his%20position.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20Lives%20are%20Equal.%20Freedom%20is%20a%20Human%20right.%20I%E2%80%99m%20raising%20my%20voice%20for%20human%20rights.%20For%20a%20humanitarian%20appeal.%20If%20you%20see%20it%20any%20other%20way.%20That%E2%80%99s%20on%20you%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhwaja%E2%80%99s%20action%20is%20said%20to%20have%20been%20driven%20by%20horrific%20events%20in%20Gaza%20which%20have%20seen%20a%20record%20number%20of%20deaths%20of%20children%20and%20civilians%20in%20such%20a%20short%20span%20of%20time%2C%20but%20he%20said%20nothing%20overtly%20about%20it%20or%20linked%20his%20gesture%20to%20that.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FUz_Khawaja%2Fstatus%2F1736680713657999851%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3EHe%20thanked%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20support%20he%20received%20this%20week.%20%E2%80%9CThank%20you%20to%20all%20those%20who%20supported%20and%20gave%20me%20love%20this%20week.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20unnoticed.%E2%80%9D%20He%20added%20by%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CNothing%20worthwhile%20is%20easy.%20History%20shows%20we%20are%20doomed%20to%20repeat%20the%20mistakes%20of%20our%20past.%20But%20together%20we%20can%20fight%20for%20a%20better%20future.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECricket%E2%80%99s%20uneasy%20relationship%20with%20standing%20up%20for%20what%20is%20right%20has%20been%20challenged%20by%20cricketers%20coming%20out%20with%20bigotry%20off-ground%2C%20necessarily%20making%20its%20way%20on%20the%20field%2C%20with%20British%20cricket%20commissioning%20reports%20on%20racial%20inequality%20and%20the%20committees%20finding%20enough%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fsport%2Fcricket%2F66032716%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520England%2520and%2520Wales%2520Cricket%2C%2522constantly%2522%2520at%2520the%2520club.%5C%22%3Esubstance%20to%20back%20the%20charges.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fsport%2F2023%2Fdec%2F21%2Fusman-khawaja-charged-by-icc-over-palestine-protest-in-australia-test%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20an%20ICC%20spokesperson%20had%20confirmed%20the%20charge%20in%20breach%20of%20the%20clothing%20and%20equipment%20regulations%20on%20Thursday.%20%E2%80%9CUsman%20displayed%20a%20personal%20message%20%5Barmband%5D%20during%20the%20first%20Test%20match%20against%20Pakistan%20without%20seeking%20the%20prior%20approval%20of%20Cricket%20Australia%20and%20the%20ICC%20to%20display%20it%2C%20as%20required%20in%20the%20regulations%20for%20personal%20messages%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20breach%20under%20the%20category%20of%20an%20%E2%80%98other%20breach%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20sanction%20for%20a%20first%20offence%20is%20a%20reprimand.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20portal%20wrote%20that%20the%20slogans%20%E2%80%9Cfreedom%20is%20a%20human%20right%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Call%20lives%20are%20equal%E2%80%9D%20were%20during%20training%20before%20the%20first%20Test%20against%20Pakistan%20in%20Perth%2C%20with%20the%20writing%20in%20red%2C%20green%20and%20black%20%E2%80%93%20the%20colours%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cricket%20establishment%E2%80%99s%20ban%20on%20apartheid%20South%20Africa%2C%20which%20proved%20to%20be%20influential%20enough%20to%20draw%20harsh%20light%20on%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20practices%2C%20and%20popularise%20anger%20against%20it%2C%20has%20since%20been%20more%20circumspect%20about%20%E2%80%98politics%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20no%20secret%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI%2C%20whose%20secretary%20is%20Jay%20Shah%2C%20incidentally%2C%20the%20son%20of%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah)%20has%20a%20high%20degree%20of%20control%20over%20ICC%20and%20Indian%20cricketers%20have%20been%20kn