't%20categorize%20them%20as%20a%20planet.%20Another%20name%20scientists%20use%20for%20them%20is%20%26quot%3Bfailed%20stars.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20leaves%20brown%20dwarfs%20in%20an%20unusual%20in-between%20state%20that%20makes%20them%20especially%20interesting%20for%20scientists%20studying%20one%20of%20astronomy's%20most%20fundamental%20questions%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20basic%20question%20you'll%20find%20in%20every%20astronomy%20textbook%20is%2C%20'%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-james-webb-telescope-image-spiral-barred-galaxy-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhat%20are%20the%20smallest%20stars%3C%2Fa%3E%3F'%20That's%20what%20we're%20trying%20to%20answer%2C%26quot%3B%20Luhman%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nasa.gov%2Fmissions%2Fwebb%2Fnasas-webb-identifies-tiniest-free-floating-brown-dwarf%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Estatement%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWebb%20sets%20another%20record%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221028%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jwst%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F565627d384307640008b593b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221019%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJWST%20has%20broken%20numerous%20records%20in%20astronomy%20since%20it%20was%20launched.%20%3Cp%3ENASA%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWebb%20is%20the%20largest%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.nasa.gov%2Fmission%2Fwebb%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emost%20powerful%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20most%20complex%20space%20telescope%20ever%20built.%20And%20its%20sensitivity%20to%20distant%20light%20in%20the%20cosmos%20was%20crucial%20for%20finding%20this%20record-breaking%20brown%20dwarf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHelping%20JWST%20out%20was%20also%20the%20fact%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-revives-her-career-mission-planner-james-webb-space-telescope-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eastronomers%20targeted%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20IC%20348%20star%20cluster.%20Part%20of%20the%20reason%20they%20chose%20this%20cluster%20is%20because%20it's%20relatively%20young%2C%20about%205%20million%20years%20old.%20(Our%20sun%20is%20about%204.5%20%3Cem%3Ebillion%3C%2Fem%3E%20years%20old.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESearching%20for%20young%2C%20new%20brown%20dwarfs%20is%20easier%20because%20these%20objects%20don't%20fuse%20hydrogen%20in%20their%20cores%2C%20like%20our%20sun.%20So%20they%20don't%20get%20nearly%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbetelgeuse-one-brightest-stars-almost-disappear-how-to-see-it-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebright%20as%20a%20star%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20brown%20dwarfs%20are%20massive%20enough%20to%20generate%20the%20right%20conditions%20to%20fuse%20a%20cousin%20of%20hydrogen%2C%20called%20deuterium.%20This%20is%20how%20they%20generate%20heat%20and%20light%20that%20telescopes%20like%20JWST%20can%20detect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20however%2C%20brown%20dwarfs%20deplete%20their%20deuterium%20reserves%2C%20and%20burn%20dimmer%2C%20as%20a%20result%2C%20making%20them%20harder%20to%20detect.%20So%20targeting%20a%20young%20star%20cluster%20with%20young%20brown%20dwarfs%20helped%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnasa-black-hole-james-webb-space-telescope-discovery-early-universe-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eastronomers%20set%20the%20record%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20brown%20dwarfs%20lack%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwe-will-never-have-sun-like-nuclear-fusion-2014-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehydrogen%20fusion%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20are%20relatively%20cool%20and%20glow%20brightest%20at%20infrared%20wavelengths.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20an%20infrared%20telescope%20like%20JWST%20is%20the%20best%20option%20for%20trying%20to%20detect%20new%20brown%20dwarfs%2C%26quot%3B%20Luhman%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20smallest%20brown%20dwarf%20on%20record%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221646%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Webb%20NIRCam%20composite%20image%20of%20Jupiter.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6303912ac9a2da00180907dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221561%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWebb%20NIRCam%20composite%20image%20of%20Jupiter.%3Cp%3ENASA%2C%20ESA%2C%20Jupiter%20ERS%20Team%3B%20image%20processing%20by%20Judy%20Schmidt%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20failed%20star%20has%20a%20mass%20of%20only%20about%20three%20to%20four%20times%20that%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjames-webb-telescope-discovery-jupiter-nasa-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJupiter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20astronomers%20reported%20in%20their%20paper.%20By%20comparison%2C%20our%20sun%20has%20a%20mass%20of%20more%20than%201%2C000%20times%20that%20of%20Jupiter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAstronomers%20didn't%20just%20find%20one%20small%20brown%20dwarf%20nestled%20in%20the%20IC%20348%20star%20cluster.%20They%20found%20three.%20The%20other%20two%20weren't%20as%20small%20but%20still%20only%20had%20masses%20of%20up%20to%20eight%20times%20that%20of%20Jupiter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20what's%20the%20point%20of%20using%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnasa-launches-james-webb-space-telescope-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eworld's%20most%20powerful%20telescope%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20seek%20out%20failed%20stars%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20considered%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.space.com%2F23798-brown-dwarfs.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emissing%20link%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20between%20stars%20and%20planets%2C%20helping%20scientists%20unravel%20many%20mysteries%20of%20the%20universe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20%26quot%3Bbrown%20dwarfs%20overlap%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnasa-planets-shrinking-atmosphere-core-radiation-exoplanet-scientists-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egiant%20planets%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20some%20physical%20properties%2C%20such%20as%20mass%20and%20temperature%2C%20so%20brown%20dwarfs%20can%20be%20used%20as%20laboratories%20for%20studying%20atmospheres%20that%20are%20similar%20to%20those%20of%20giant%20planets%2C%26quot%3B%20Luhman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20also%20important%20for%20understanding%20stellar%20formation%2C%20in%20general.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20ask%2C%20how%20does%20the%20star%20formation%20process%20operate%20at%20such%20very%2C%20very%20small%20masses%3F%26quot%3B%20Catarina%20Alves%20de%20Oliveira%20of%20the%20European%20Space%20Agency%2C%20principal%20investigator%20on%20the%20observing%20program%2C%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20discovery%20raises%20new%20questions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EScientists%20are%20surprised%20by%20this%20discovery%20because%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20theoretically%20prove%20the%20existence%20of%20such%20small%20brown%20dwarfs%2C%20per%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20small%20cloud%2C%20it's%20harder%20to%20collapse%20due%20to%20low%20gravity.%20So%20theoretically%2C%20if%20it%20has%20gained%20a%20mass%20equivalent%20to%20a%20giant%20planet%2C%20it%20should%20become%20a%20planet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20what%20causes%20it%20to%20become%20a%20brown%20dwarf%3F%20That's%20a%20cosmic%20mystery%20that%20remains%20to%20be%20solved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUp%20next%2C%20astronomers%20would%20like%20to%20conduct%20longer%20surveys%20with%20JWST%20that%20could%20help%20detect%20even%20smaller%20objects%2C%20down%20to%20the%20same%20mass%20as%20Jupiter%2C%20per%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWill%20astronomers%20find%20an%20even%20smaller%20brown%20dwarf%3F%20Perhaps%2C%20if%20astronomers%20keep%20discovering%20more%20of%20these%20bizarre%20outliers%2C%20it%20could%20give%20more%20clues%20to%20this%20cosmic%20mystery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20possible%20that%20brown%20dwarfs%20exist%20at%20even%20smaller%20masses%2C%20but%20they%20have%20not%20been%20detected%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20Luhman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjames-webb-space-telescope-discovers-smallest-brown-dwarf-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703331781000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65860063a79e5746976cece3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjames-webb-space-telescope-discovers-smallest-brown-dwarf-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22NASA's%20Webb%20telescope%20was%20able%20to%20spot%20an%20object%2C%20the%20smallest%20of%20its%20kind%2C%20from%201%2C000%20light%20years%20away.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Rupendra%20Brahambhatt)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjames-webb-space-telescope-discovers-smallest-brown-dwarf-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Taiwan%20detects%207%20Chinese%20military%20aircraft%2C%202%20naval%20ships%20around%20nation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703331582000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106234791%2Cimgsize-346299.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Ftaiwan-detects-7-chinese-military-aircraft-2-naval-ships-around-nation%2Farticleshow%2F106234667.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106234667.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Ftaiwan-detect