and%20cleanliness.%20And%20if%20it%20had%20those%20two%20things%20it%20was%20great.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETogether%2C%20the%20friends%20visited%20Chiang%20Mai%2C%20Thailand%3B%20Petra%2C%20Jordan%3B%20Salzburg%2C%20Austria%3B%20Cape%20Town%2C%20South%20Africa%3B%20and%20Byron%20Bay%2C%20Australia%2C%20along%20with%20many%20other%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jordan%20Carlyle%20and%20Christen%20Puckett%20at%20the%20Gljufrabui%20waterfall%20in%20Iceland.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6570f4ba58e7c0c29a2a7669%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20two%20friends%20visited%20the%20Gljufrabui%20waterfall%20in%20Iceland.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Christen%20Puckett%20and%20Jordan%20Carlyle%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECarlyle%20and%20Puckett%20have%20shared%20their%20travel%20experiences%20in%20videos%2C%20including%20on%20their%20TikTok%20account%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40wheretonextyall%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%40wheretonextyall%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Puckett%20said%20their%20intention%20wasn't%20to%20be%20travel%20influencers.%20Instead%2C%20she%20said%20they%20wanted%20to%20document%20their%20trip%20for%20friends%20and%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20they%20were%20able%20to%20go%20on%20a%20six-month%20trip%20and%20what%20advice%20they%20would%20give%20others%20who%20want%20to%20quit%20or%20take%20a%20career%20break%20to%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20how%20they%20stayed%20within%20their%20budget%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Christen%20Puckett%20and%20Jordan%20Carlyle%20with%20an%20elephant%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6570f8dd58e7c0c29a2a78f4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChristen%20Puckett%20and%20Jordan%20Carlyle%20visit%20an%20elephant%20sanctuary%20in%20Chiang%20Mai%2C%20Thailand.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Christen%20Puckett%20and%20Jordan%20Carlyle%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esavings%20budget%20of%20%2425%2C000%20each%2C%20Puckett%20said%20they%20committed%20to%20%241%2C000%20a%20week%20during%20their%20travels%20for%20all%20expenses.%20Puckett%20said%20they%20found%20%26quot%3Byou%20can%20easily%20get%20away%20actually%20with%20less%20than%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20they%20did%20spend%20more%20or%20less%20some%20weeks.%20Puckett%20said%20that's%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20we%20chose%20to%20stay%20in%20countries%20that%20were%20more%20affordable%20longer%2C%20such%20as%20Southeast%20Asia.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etheir%20accommodation%20at%20a%20hostel%20in%20Bangkok%20from%20September%206%20to%20September%207%20was%20%2428.%20However%2C%20staying%20at%20a%20place%20in%20Byron%20Bay%20from%20September%2027%20to%20October%202%2C%20ended%20up%20costing%20%24690%2C%20averaging%20out%20to%20%24138%20a%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPuckett%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid%20staying%20for%20free%20with%20new%20friends%20they%20met%20also%20helped.%20Carlyle%20and%20Puckett%20also%20would%20stay%20in%20hostels%20and%20noted%20this%20is%20also%20a%20good%20way%20to%20meet%20others%20while%20traveling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20go%20from%20America%20where%20you%20have%20these%20big%20rooms%2C%20and%20you%20think%20that%20you%20need%20these%20massive%20bathrooms%20and%20bedrooms%20to%20sleep%20in%20and%20to%20work%2C%20and%20what%20you%20realize%20is%20your%20whole%20perspective%20changes%2C%26quot%3B%20Puckett%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20spent%20our%20entire%20days%20exploring%2C%20and%20then%20we%20would%20come%20back%20and%20go%20to%20bed.%20And%20so%20what%20we%20realized%20is%20we%20didn't%20need%20to%20spend%20that%20money%20on%20accommodations.