hasn't%20felt%20pressure%20to%20go%20under%20the%20knife.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHealthcare%20is%20extremely%20affordable%20compared%20to%20the%20US%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETeng%20said%20when%20she%20first%20arrived%20in%20Korea%20she%20had%20to%20visit%20the%20doctor%20while%20uninsured.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20coworkers%20were%20like%2C%20'It's%20going%20to%20be%20so%20expensive%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20having%20a%20check-up%20for%20her%20fever%20and%20sore%20throat%2C%20Teng%20was%20surprised%20to%20be%20handed%20a%20bill%20for%20the%20equivalent%20of%20%248.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20BI%20her%20coworkers%20said%20that%20if%20she%20had%20been%20insured%2C%20the%20bill%20would%20have%20been%20roughly%20%243.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20night%20clubs%20don't%20allow%20foreigners%20to%20enter%2C%20according%20to%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETeng%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETeng%20said%20that%20Korea%20is%20a%20homogenous%20country%2C%20so%20while%20acceptance%20of%20foreigners%20is%20getting%20better%2C%20it's%20still%20a%20new%20adjustment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20BI%20there%20are%20foreigner-friendly%20areas%20in%20Seoul%2C%20which%20are%20parts%20of%20the%20city%20where%20a%20lot%20of%20foreigners%20live%20and%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20a%20club%20in%20the%20area%20had%20a%20sign%20saying%20that%20unless%20entrants%20had%20a%20card%20which%20is%20given%20to%20Koreans%20and%20Korean%20nationals%20abroad%2C%20they%20wouldn't%20be%20permitted%20entry.%20%26quot%3BWhich%20essentially%20means%20no%20foreigners%20are%20allowed%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20Teng%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amnesty.org%2Fen%2Flatest%2Fnews%2F2021%2F08%2Fsouth-korea-lawmakers-must-pass-landmark-anti-discrimination-act%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediscrimination%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Korea%2C%20so%20technically%2C%20that%20is%20allowed%2C%26quot%3B%20Teng%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20city%20has%20foreigner-friendly%20clubs%2C%20but%20others%20aren't%20always%20forthright%20about%20denying%20entry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERent%20can%20be%20as%20low%20as%20%24120%20a%20month%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20an%20interesting%20system%20in%20Korea%20with%20housing%20and%20there's%20something%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fsouth-koreas-jeonse-rent-free-renters-hit-by-property-downturn-2023-02-21%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejeonse%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20wolse%2C%26quot%3B%20Teng%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETeng%20said%20jeonse%20is%20when%20someone%20gets%20a%20large%20loan%20from%20the%20bank%2C%20but%20they%20pay%20the%20interest%20back%20rather%20than%20the%20loan%2C%20and%20this%20makes%20rental%20payments%20very%20small.%20She%20added%20that%20from%20her%20experience%2C%20this%20is%20an%20option%20usually%20only%20given%20to%20Koreans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20pay%20the%20deposit%20and%20my%20monthly%20rent%2C%26quot%3B%20Teng%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20is%20called%20wolse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20the%20average%20rent%20here%20per%20month%20is%20maybe%20like%20700%2C000-800%2C000%20won%2C%26quot%3B%20Teng%20told%20BI.%20This%20is%20around%20%24540-%24610.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETeng%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fsouth-koreas-millennials-lives-arent-different-dire-realities-squid-game-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egoshiwons%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20small%20closet%20rooms%20that%20are%20popular%20among%20young%20people%20who%20move%20to%20Korea%20to%20study.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20get%20those%20for%20200%2C000-300%2C000%20a%20month%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added%2C%20which%20is%20around%20%24150-%24230.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20basement%20apartments%20depicted%20in%20the%20Korean%20film%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-best-picture-winner-parasite-has-made-box-office-2020-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BParasite%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20do%20still%20exist%2C%20but%20many%20are%20refurbished%20and%20are%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20those%20on%20the%20silver%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETeng%20told%20BI%20a%20friend%20of%20hers%20pays%20about%20%24700%20for%20a%20basement%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFood%20variety%20is%20limited%2C%20and%20vegans%20may%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20source%20different%20options%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETeng%20said%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224041%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Someone%20picking%20out%20milk%20in%20a%20Korean%20grocery%20store.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65708e777a3c8094d5da11b9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222622%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETeng%20said%20dairy%20alternatives%20weren't%20mainstream%20in%20Korea%20before%20the%20pandemic.%3Cp%3EPARK%20JI-HWAN%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFruit%20here%20is%20quite%20expensive%2C%26quot%3B%20Teng%20said.%20She%20added%20that%20on%20a%20recent%20trip%20to%20a%20grocery%20store%20it%20was%20roughly%20%2420%20for%20a%20few%20apples.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20miss%20my%20variety%20of%20apples%2C%20there's%20not%20a%20variety%20of%20produce%2C%26quot%3B%20Teng%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20reason%20for%20these%20high%20prices%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20variety%20is%20that%20produce%20is%20rarely%20imported%20into%20Korea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20those%20with%20dietary%20restrictions%20like%20gluten%20free%20or%20vegan%20diets%20may%20find%20it%20difficult%2C%20as%20these%20diets%20aren't%20widely%20followed%20outside%20large%20cities%20like%20Seoul%20and%20Busan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20get%20oat%20milk%20until%20post-Covid.%20Alternative%20milk%20options%20in%20coffee%20shops%2C%20that's%20now%20becoming%20a