%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20face%20of%20it%2C%20some%20decisions%20might%20look%20straightforward%20but%20things%20won't%20be%20as%20easy%20as%20it%20seems%20for%20the%20Indian%20team%20management%2C%20which%20will%20again%20have%20to%20make%20unpopular%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMukesh%20or%20Prasidh%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centurion%20track%20has%20primarily%20been%20a%20pace%20bowler's%20paradise%20--%20hard%20and%20bouncy%20with%20humidity%20that%20aids%20reverse%20swing%20during%20the%20latter%20half%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20if%20one%20is%20talking%20about%20lateral%20movement%2C%20then%20Mukesh%2C%20who%20has%20already%20made%20his%20Test%20debut%20in%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20walks%20straight%20into%20the%20playing%20XI.%20But%20the%20Bengal%20seamer%20hasn't%20looked%20in%20the%20best%20of%20form%20during%20the%20white%20ball%20leg%20of%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20151%20wickets%20from%2040%20first-class%20games%2C%20red%20ball%20cricket%20is%20where%20Mukesh%20feels%20at%20home%20and%20has%20an%20average%20of%2021%20plus%20runs%20per%20wicket.%20His%20strike-rate%20remains%20a%20very%20decent%2048%20balls%20per%20wicket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20Mukesh%20is%20a%20like%20a%20workhorse%2C%20who%20can%20bowl%20long%20spells%20and%20has%20also%20been%20known%20to%20use%20reverse%20swing%20during%20his%20post%20tea%20spells%20in%20Ranji%20Trophy%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20advantage%20is%20channel%20bowling%20--%20right%20on%20the%20line%20-%20in%20and%20around%20the%20off-stump%20corridor%20and%20keeping%20it%20at%20fuller%20length.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukesh's%20nearest%20competitor%20is%20one%20of%20Dravid's%20favourite%20and%20a%20fellow%20Bangalore%20man%20Prasidh%2C%20whose%20hit-the-deck%20stuff%20is%20ideal%20for%20the%20Supersport%20Park.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrasidh%2C%20who%20hasn't%20even%20played%2015%20first-class%20games%20since%20his%20