0Topa%20Mastandara%2C%20Mehmood%20Ahmed%2C%20said%20that%20the%20slain%20persons%20were%20among%20eight%20persons%20who%20were%20detained%20by%20the%20Army%20from%20their%20residences%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20deadly%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocals%20and%20families%20of%20the%20deceased%20alleged%20that%20they%20were%20tortured%20to%20death%20by%20the%20Army.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20army%20men%20picked%20up%20several%20civilians%20from%20their%20homes%20on%20Friday%20morning%20besides%20summoning%20a%20few%20of%20them%20to%20their%20camp%20over%20the%20phone%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Muhammad%20Siddique%2C%20uncle%20of%20Showkat%2C%20the%20youngest%20among%20the%20three%20dead%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddique%2C%20who%20is%20also%20Panch%20of%20the%20locality%2C%20said%20that%20he%20rang%20up%20several%20local%20politicians%20and%20officials%20to%20help%20them%20in%20getting%20them%20released%20from%20custody%20after%20they%20were%20detained.%20%E2%80%9CI%20told%20them%20that%20they%20are%20being%20beaten%20up%20but%20nobody%20came%20to%20their%20rescue%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fthree-army-soldiers-killed-in-anti-militancy-operation-in-jks-poonch%5C%22%3EFive%20Army%20Soldiers%20Killed%20in%20Anti-Militancy%20Operation%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Poonch%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20independently%20verify%20his%20claim.%C2%A0He%20said%20they%20were%20mercilessly%20killed%20by%20Army%20men%20in%20the%20Mall%20post%20camp.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20asked%20officials%20why%20they%20were%20killed%3F%20They%20told%20us%20that%20they%20have%20been%20killed%20due%20to%20their%20%E2%80%98mistake%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20dead%20bodies%20were%20handed%20over%20to%20them%20at%20around%208%20am%20today%20for%20last%20rites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20not%20allowing%20anybody%2C%20including%20the%20media%2C%20to%20enter%20the%20village.%20They%20have%20deployed%20CRPF%20men%20in%20large%20strength%20in%20the%20locality.%20This%20is%20the%20height%20of%20injustice%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddique%20said%20they%20were%20innocent%20and%20had%20not%20even%20remote%20links%20with%20any%20subversive%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20nothing%20adverse%20against%20them.%20There%20is%20not%20even%20an%20application%20against%20them%20in%20the%20police%20station%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoor%20Ahmad%2C%20brother%20of%20deceased%20Safeer%20Hussain%2C%20said%20that%20he%20was%20detained%20by%20Army%20men%20from%20his%20home%20on%20Friday.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20shocked%20to%20know%20in%20the%20evening%20that%20they%20had%20been%20killed.%20They%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20custody%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoor%20said%20that%20he%20was%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20talk.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20in%20shock.%20I%20will%20talk%20to%20you%20after%20the%20funeral%20prayers%20are%20over%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20purported%20video%20clips%20of%20the%20detained%20men%20being%20tortured%20show%20army%20soldiers%20spraying%20chilli%20powder%20on%20their%20buttocks.%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EGand%20Mein%20Dal%20Es%20Ko%20Mirchi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Put%20chilli%20in%20his%20anus)%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20soldier%20can%20be%20heard%20saying%20in%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20also%20shows%20a%20young%20boy%2C%20who%20is%20lying%20motionless%20on%20the%20ground%20while%20another%20man%20can%20be%20seen%20moving%20his%20hands%20helplessly%20before%20being%20stripped%20and%20sprayed%20with%20chilli%20powder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20video%20shows%20army%20soldiers%20pushing%20and%20beating%20up%20a%20man%20with%20what%20looks%20like%20a%20plastic%20cane%20while%20he%20is%20pleading%20with%20them%20to%20spare%20him.%20An%20army%20man%20could%20be%20seen%20sitting%20with%20jackboots%20on%20the%20arms%20of%20a%20civilian%20lying%20motionless%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20independently%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20these%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMobile%20internet%20has%20been%20suspended%20in%20Poonch%20district%20following%20the%20alleged%20custodial%20deaths.%20Preparations%20are%20underway%20to%20conduct%20their%20last%20rites%20with%20top%20officials%20of%20civil%20and%20police%20administration%20rushing%20to%20the%20area%20while%20restrictions%20have%20been%20imposed%20to%20avoid%20any%20law%20and%20order%20disturbances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20visit%20their%20village%20because%20there%20are%20restrictions%20here.%20But%20I%20have%20been%20told%20that%20the%20five%20other%20civilians%20are%20admitted%20in%20the%20army%20hospital.%20We%20are%20preparing%20to%20conduct%20the%20last%20rites%20of%20the%20deceased%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rafiq%2C%20the%20Sarpanch%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20all%20labourers%20who%20struggled%20to%20make%20a%20living.%20I%20guarantee%20that%20they%20were%20not%20involved%20in%20any%20illegal%20activities.%20It%20is%20tragic%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Divisional%20Commissioner%20Jammu%2C%20Ramesh%20Kumar%2C%20said%20that%20he%20was%20gathering%20details%20about%20how%20the%20civilians%20died.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20collecting%20details%2C%20will%20share%20it%20later%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20population%20of%20around%20200-250%20population%20comprising%20largely%20Gujjar%20and%20Bakkerwal%20tribes%2C%20the%20village%20of%20Topa%20Mastandara%20is%20situated%20in%20the%20higher%20reaches%20of%20Dera%20Ki%20Gali-Bufliaz%20axis%20where%20two%20Army%20vehicles%20were%20ambushed%20earlier%20this%20week.%20The%20village%20is%20locally%20famous%20for%20hosting%20the%20shrine%20of%20Topa%20Peer%2C%20a%20Sufi%20saint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20was%20claimed%20by%20the%20Peoples%20Anti-Fascist%20Front%2C%20which%20officials%20believe%20is%20an%20offshoot%20of%20Pakistan-based%20Jaish-e-Mohammad.%20The%20attackers%20had%20mutilated%20the%20bodies%20of%20two%20soldiers%20and%20decamped%20with%20rifles%20of%20some%20of%20the%20slain%20soldiers%2C%20prompting%20massive%20searches%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20more%20soldiers%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20attack%20and%20their%20condition%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20stable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20have%20shut%20down%20a%20strategic%20road%20connecting%20Poonch%20and%20Rajouri%20districts%20to%20scale%20up%20the%20search%20operations.%20Choppers%20have%20been%20pressed%20into%20service%20to%20carry%20out%20surveillance%20sorties%20while%20hi-tech%20gadgetry%20has%20been%20activated%20to%20trace%20the%20attackers%20who%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20hiding%20in%20the%20dense%20forests%20in%20Surankote%2C%20which%20falls%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirector%20General%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%2C%20R%20R%20Swain%2C%20General%20Officer%20Commanding%20(GoC)%2C%20XVI%20Corps%2C%20Lt%20Gen%20Sandeep%20Jain%20and%20a%20team%20of%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20visited%20the%20site%20of%20the%20attack%20in%20Poonch%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoonch%20and%20Rajouri%20districts%20are%20part%20of%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%20in%20the%20Jammu%20division%20which%20has%20witnessed%20a%20dramatic%20spike%20in%20militancy-related%20incidents%20in%20the%20years%20after%20the%20Union%20government%20read%20down%20Article%20370%20and%20downgraded%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20into%20two%20union%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20violence%20has%20subsided%20in%20Kashmir%20valley%20after%20years%20of%20shutdowns%2C%20clashes%20and%20encounters%20involving%20civilians%2C%20militants%20and%20security%20forces%2C%20the%20theatre%20of%20insurgency%20has%20shifted%20to%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%20where%2024%20militants%20were%20killed%20this%20year%20while%2021%20army%20soldiers%20also%20laid%20down%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2010%20civilians%20have%20also%20been%20killed%20in%20conflict-related%20violence%20in%20the%20twin%20districts%20this%20year%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20official%20data%2C%20124%20people%2C%20including%2083%20militants%20and%2028%20security%20personnel%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20due%20to%20the%20prevailing%20security%20situation%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20deceased%20are%20two%20army%20and%20police%20officers%2C%20including%20a%20Colonel%20and%20a%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20who%20lost%20their%20lives%20in%20the%20week-long%20Kokernag%20encounter%20in%20south%20Kashmir%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20three%20labourers%20from%20Rajouri%20district%20were%20killed%20in%20a%20staged%20gun%20battle%20by%20the%20Army%20in%20Amshipora%20village%20of%20south%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Shopian%20district%20and%20passed%20off%20as%20terrorists%2C%20reportedly%20for%20cash%20reward%20and%20quick%20promotion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20police%20investigation%2C%20an%20Army%20Captain%20identified%20as%20Bhoopendra%20Singh%20alias%20Major%20Basheer%20Khan%20had%20abducted%20the%20three%20young%20men%20in%20a%20private%20car%20from%20their%20rented%20accommodation%20at%20Chowgam%20Shopian%2C%20killed%20them%20and%20later%20planted%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20weapons%20and%20material%20on%20their%20dead%20bodies%20and%20tried%20to%20tag%20them%20as%20hardcore%20terrorists.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703325532000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fcivilians-killed-in-the-aftermath-of-poonch-terror-attac