inside%20the%20district%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ITLF%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20comes%20a%20day%20after%20the%20Manipur%20government%20had%20issued%20a%20statement%20noting%20that%20two%20key%20highways%20from%20Imphal%20to%20Churachandpur%20and%20Mao%2C%20through%20Kangpokpi%20district%2C%20and%20the%20routes%20were%20now%20operational.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20for%20the%20information%20of%20all%2C%20that%20the%20Imphal%20%E2%80%93%20Kangpokpi%20%E2%80%93%20Mao%20Highway%20and%20the%20Imphal%20Bishnupur%20-Churachandpur%20Highway%20are%20operational%20and%20open%20for%20use%20by%20all.%20For%20convenience%20and%20security%20of%20the%20people%20using%20the%20highways%2C%20additional%20security%20forces%20have%20been%20deployed%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20Manipur%20home%20department%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fkey-routes-from-manipurs-imphal-made-operational-additional-security-deployed-2479499-2023-12-23%5C%22%3Ehad%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ITLF%E2%80%99s%20decision%20would%20prevent%20the%20state%20government%20from%20posting%20more%20forces%20and%20opening%20the%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20local%20Kuki%20groups%20in%20Kangpoki%20district%2C%20which%20is%20on%20the%20opposite%20side%20of%20Churachandpur%20with%20Imphal%20Valley%20in%20between%2C%20have%20also%20announced%20a%20lockdown%20of%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ITLF%20statement%20came%20two%20days%20after%20the%20bodies%20of%2087%20Kuki-Zo%20victims%20of%20the%20ongoing%20ethnic%20clashes%20were%20buried%20at%20one%20location%20in%20Churachandpur%20district%20and%20following%20recent%20clashes%20that%20erupted%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703324572000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F08131052%2FF7SQIIebEAAHp2K.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-kuki