20the%20world%20to%20follow.%20The%20concept%20was%20eventually%20accepted%20by%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20a%20year%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20introduction%20of%20'Electra%20Stumps'%20has%20created%20a%20lot%20of%20buzz%2C%20Sixers%20all-rounder%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Tom%20Curran%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64567-thomas-kevin-curran-playerprofile%5C%22%3ETom%20Curran%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20hogged%20all%20the%20limelight%20with%20his%20recent%20act%20in%20the%20BBL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurran%20has%20been%20banned%20from%20four%20BBL%20matches%20after%20being%20found%20guilty%20of%20intimidating%20an%20umpire%20in%20a%20pre-match%20dispute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20player%20was%20involved%20in%20an%20argument%20with%20an%20official%20before%20the%20Sixers'%20penultimate%20match%20against%20the%20Hobart%20Hurricanes%20on%20December%2011%20in%20Launceston%2C%20when%20he%20attempted%20to%20finish%20a%20practice%20run-up%20on%20the%20pitch%20during%20the%20warm-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fourth%20umpire%2C%20who%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20supervising%20the%20pitch%20during%20pauses%20in%20play%2C%20tried%20to%20stop%20Curran%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20Englishman%20being%20charged%20with%20a%20Level%203%20infraction%20under%20Cricket%20Australia's%20code%20of%20conduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Brisbane%20Heat%20are%20top%20of%20the%20BBL%20points%20table%20with%20seven%20points%20from%20four%20matches.%20On%20the%20contrary.%20Melbourne%20Stars%20occupy%20the%20foot%20of%20the%20table%20with%20no%20points%20in%20two%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703322900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F1tm526n_electra-stumps-806_625x300_23_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Felectra-stumps-heres-all-you-need-to-know-about-big-bash-leagues-brand-new-feature-4726910%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Having