0Yanika%20inside%20a%20room%2C%20hurled%20abuses%20at%20her%2C%20pulled%20her%20hair%20and%20assaulted%20her.%20The%20complaint%20claims%20that%20Yanika%20is%20unable%20to%20hear%20properly%20because%20of%20the%20assault.%20Bindra%20allegedly%20broke%20her%20phone%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20domestic%20abuse%2C%20Bindra%20has%20also%20been%20involved%20in%20other%20controversies%3B%20most%20recently%20being%20accused%20of%20running%20a%20%26quot%3Bscam%26quot%3B%20by%20fellow%20YouTuber%20and%20motivational%20speaker%20Sandeep%20Maheshwari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EVivek%20Bindra%20vs%20Sandeep%20Maheshwari%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYouTuber%20Sandeep%20Maheshwari%20recently%20released%20a%20video%20titled%20'Big%20Scam%20Exposed'%2C%20accusing%20Bindra%20of%20running%20a%20course%20akin%20to%20multi-level%20marketing.%20The%20alleged%20scam%20involves%20taking%20vast%20sums%20of%20money%20from%20students%20to%20teach%20them%20%26quot%3Bbusiness%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20amounts%20to%20nearly%20Rs%20500%20crore.%20Bindra%20responded%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20challenging%20Mr%20Maheshwari%20and%20denying%20any%20wrongdoing.%20The%20conflict%20intensified%20as%20Bindra%20alleged%20threats%20against%20his%20legal%20team%20and%20the%20intrusion%20of%20Mr%20Maheshwari's%20house%20by%20his%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EControversy%20Over%20Sikh%20Community%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202022%2C%20Bindra%20faced%20backlash%20from%20the%20Sikh%20community%20over%20an%20animated%20depiction%20of%20Guru%20Gobind%20Singh%20in%20one%20of%20his%20videos.%20The%20controversy%20prompted%20demands%20for%20an%20apology%2C%20and%20Bindra%20had%20to%20apologise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EVivek%20Bindra%20vs%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20the%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20(IMA)%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20Bindra.%20The%20IMA%20accused%20Bindra%20of%20usin