20the%20franchise%20in%20the%20upcoming%20season%20of%20IPL%2C%20replacing%20long-serving%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandya%20had%20played%20seven%20seasons%20of%20IPL%20for%20Mumbai%20before%20being%20released%20prior%20to%20the%202022%20season.%20After%20joining%20Gujarat%20Titans%2C%20Pandya%20led%20the%20side%20to%20back-to-back%20IPL%20finals%2C%20including%20earning%20them%20the%20trophy%20in%20their%20debut%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHardik%20missed%20the%20recently%20concluded%20white-ball%20leg%20of%20the%20South%20Africa%20tour%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20T20I%20series%20against%20Australia.%20In%20his%20absence%2C%20Suryakumar%20led%20India%20to%20a%204-1%20series%20win%20over%20Australia%2C%20while%20the%20T20I%20series%20ended%20in%20a%20draw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20true%2C%20the%20latest%20development%20could%20be%20a%20huge%20blow%20for%20both%20Team%20India%20and%20MI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20IPL%20auction%2C%20MI%20bought%20South%20Africa%20pacer%20Gerald%20Coetzee%20as%20their%20first%20buy.%20Coetzee%2C%20who%20had%20a%20base%20price%20of%20Rs%202%20crore%2C%20went%20to%20MI%20for%20Rs%205%20crore%20after%20bidding%20wars%20with%20RCB%20and%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20(LSG).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMI%20further%20strengthened%20their%20pace%20battery%20with%20the%20addition%20of%20Sri%20Lankan%20pacers%20Dilshan%20Madushanka%20and%20Nuwan%20Thushara.%C2%A0MI%20also%20waited%20until%20the%20accelerator%20round%20to%20rope%20in%20Afghanistan%20all-rounder%20Mohammad%20Nabi%20at%20his%20base%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMI%20Retained%20players%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20Sharma%2C%20Dewald%20Brevis%2C%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%2C%20Ishan%20Kishan%2C%20N.%20Tilak%20Varma%2C%20Tim%20David%2C%20Vishnu%20Vinod%2C%20Arjun%20Tendulkar%2C%20Shams%20Mulani%2C%20Nehal%20Wadhera%2C%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%2C%20Kumar%20Kartikeya%2C%20Piyush%20Chawla%2C%20Akash%20Madhwal%2C%20Jason%20Behrendorff%2C%20Romario%20Shepherd%20(from%20LSG)%2C%20Hardik%20Pandya%20(C)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMI%20players%20bought%20at%20IPL%202024%20auction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGerald%20Coetzee%20(Rs.%205%20crore)%2C%20Dilshan%20Madushanka%20(Rs.%204.60%20crore)%2C%20Shreyas%20Gopal%20(Rs.%2020%20lakh)%2C%20Nuwan%20Thushara%20(Rs.%204.80%20crore)%2C%20Naman%20Dhir%20(Rs.%2020%20lakh)%2C%20Anshul%20Kamboj%20(Rs.%2020%20lakh)%2C%20Mohammad%20Nabi%20(Rs.%201.5%20crore)%2C%20Shivalik%20Sharma%20(Rs.%2020%20lakh)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703320560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fh12ssaio_hardik-pandya-x_625x300_28_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fmumbai-indians-captain-hardik-pandya-may-be-ruled-out-of-ipl-2024-due-to-injury-sources-4727576%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hardik%20Pandya%20could%20miss%20the%20upcoming%20season%20of%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20due%20to%20an%20ankle%20injury%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fmumbai-indians-captain-hardik-pandya-may-be-ruled-out-of-ipl-2024-due-to-injury-sources-4727576%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fmumbai-indians-captain-hardik-pandya-may-be-ruled-out-of-ipl-2024-due-to-injury-sources-4727576%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fmumbai-indians-captain-hardik-pandya-may-be-ruled-out-of-ipl-2024-due-to-injury-sources-4727576%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Is%20The%20Most%20Deleted%20App%20Of%202023.%20The%20Name%20Is...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWorldwide%20smartphone%20users%20exhibit%20swift%20decisions%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20downloading%20or%20uninstalling%20applications.%20The%20duration%20of%20retention%20largely%20hinges%20on%20user%20preferences%20and%20the%20popularity%20of%20the%20app.%20TRG%20Data%20Centers%20recently%20conducted%20an%20analysis%20of%20smartphone%20users'%20app%20uninstallation%20habits%2C%20unearthing%20some%20unexpected%20findings.%20The%20report%20delves%20into%20the%20data%20to%20offer%20insights%20into%20user%20behavior%20regarding%20the%20installation%20and%20removal%20of%20mobile%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.trgdatacenters.com%2Fresource%2Fthe-most-deleted-social-media-apps-in-2023%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20are%204.8%20billion%20social%20media%20users%20worldwide%2C%20which%20represents%2059.9%25%20of%20the%20global%20population%20and%2092.7%25%20of%20all%20internet%20users.%20Those%20that%20use%20social%20media%20use%20an%20average%20of%206.7%20different%20networks%20each%20month%2C%20spending%20an%20average%20of%202%20hours%20and%2024%20minutes%20on%20them%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20findings%20in%20the%20report%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20Instagram%20emerged%20as%20the%20social%20media%20platform%20most%20users%20were%20inclined%20to%20remove.%20The%20data%20indicates%20that%20in%202023%2C%20a%20staggering%20number%20of%20over%201%20million%20individuals%20globally%20were%20actively%20searching%20for%20'how%20to%20delete%20my%20Instagram%20account'%20each%20month.%20This%20equates%20to%20more%20than%2012%2C500%20searches%20per%20100%2C000%20people%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20despite%20its%20origins%20as%20a%20digital%20scrapbook%2C%20Instagram%20has%20consistently%20maintained%20its%20position%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20social%20media%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20further%20states%20that%20despite%20all%20this%20trend%2C%20the%20app%20still%20boasts%202.4%20billion%20active%20users%20worldwide.%20However%2C%20if%20a%20million%20people%20continue%20to%20seek%20deletion%20of%20their%20accounts%20every%20month%2C%20the%20'Instagrammable'%20bubble%20could%20burst%2C%20potentially%20altering%20its%20landscape%20within%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20followed%20by%20Snapchat%2C%20which%20first%20launched%20in%202011.%20Almost%20130%2C000%20people%20have%20looked%20to%20delete%20their%20Snapchat%20account%20per%20month%20this%20year.%20And%20while%20this%20is%20significantly%20less%20than%20Instagram%2C%20it's%20still%20a%20large%20part%20of%20their%20750%20million%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703320140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F186j3rl8_social-media-app_625x300_23_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fthis-is-the-most-deleted-app-of-2023-the-name-is-4727714%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20social%20media%20has%20become%20deeply%20woven%20into%20our%20lives%2C%20many%20platforms%20faced%20significant%20challenges%20in%20staying%20relevant%20in%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fthis-is-the-most-deleted-app-of-2023-the-name-is-4727714%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fthis-is-the-most-deleted-app-of-2023-the-name-is-4727714%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fthis-is-the-most-deleted-app-of-2023-the-name-is-4727714%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BTS'%20Jungkook%20creates%20history%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703320040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106231105%2Cimgsize-163808.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fk-pop%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fbts-jungkook-creates-history-as-the-first-korean-soloist-to-chart-an-album-for-7-consecutive-weeks-on-the-uks-official-albums-chart%2Farticleshow%2F106231166.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indi