0alliance%20partners%20propping%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge's%20name%20for%20the%20top%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20RJD%20leader%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20said%20there%20is%20no%20fight%20in%20Bihar.%20Asked%20about%20reports%20of%20rift%20in%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWho%20is%20saying%20all%20this%3F%20Go%20and%20ask%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JDU%20has%20also%20brushed%20aside%20any%20reports%20of%20problems%20in%20the%20alliance%2C%20with%20its%20national%20president%2C%20Lallan%20Singh%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BAll's%20well%20in%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%20We%20will%20decide%20on%20seat%20sharing%20in%20a%20week.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Union%20Minister%20and%20BJP%20leader%20Giriraj%20Singh%2C%20in%20an%20explosive%20revelation%2C%20said%20RJD%20chief%20Lalu%20Yadav%20has%20told%20him%20that%20the%20JDU%20will%20soon%20merge%20with%20the%20RJD%20in%20the%20state.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20politicise%20this.%20But%20Lalu%20Yadav%20and%20I%20go%20way%20back.%20He%20has%20told%20me%20that%20the%20JDU%20will%20merge%20with%20the%20RJD%20soon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDismissing%20the%20BJP%20leader's%20remarks%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20(the%20BJP)%20want%20to%20attribute%20their%20thoughts%20to%20others.%20They%20have%20to%20do%20this%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20limelight.%20If%20they%20don't%20say%20these%20things%2C%20will%20you%20give%20them%20space%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20also%20shrugged%20off%20the%20BJP's%20claims%20that%20it%20will%20sweep%202024%20with%2050%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20votes%20and%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BPeople%20talk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20fourth%20meeting%20of%20the%20Opposition%20alliance%2C%20held%20in%20Delhi%20on%20December%2019%2C%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20proposed%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge's%20name%20as%20the%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate%20of%20the%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%2012%20of%20the%20participating%20parties%20backed%20her%20given%20Mr%20Kharge%20is%20a%20prominent%20Dalit%20face%20in%20the%20Opposition.%20Ms%20Banerjee's%20proposal%20also%20found%20unexpected%20support%20from%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20is%20known%20for%20being%20mostly%20out-of-sync%20with%20the%20Congress.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20chance%20to%20have%20India's%20first%20Dalit%20Prime%20Minister%2C%26quot%3B%20sources%20quoted%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%2C%20however%2C%20downplayed%20this%20and%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20win%20first%20and%20think%20what%20to%20do%20to%20win.%20What%20is%20the%20point%20of%20discussing%20PM%20before%20having%20MPs%3F%20We%20will%20try%20to%20get%20a%20majority%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20massive%20approval%20for%20Mr%20Kharge%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20an%20indication%20of%20his%20stature%20among%20the%20Opposition%20leaders%2C%20it%20is%20also%20seen%20as%20a%20snub%20to%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20-%20the%20Opposition%20has%20been%20divided%20over%20his%20candidature%20for%20the%20top%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703315220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fc919r8e_tejashwi-yadav-650_625x300_30_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fall-is-well-bihar-ruling-alliance-denies-nitish-kumar-upset-india-rift-4727394%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bihar's%20ruling%20coalition%20partners%2C%20the%20JD(U)%20and%20the%20RJD%2C%20put%20up%20a%20united%20front%2C%20reiterating%20%26quot%3Ball%20is%20well%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Opposition's%20mega%20INDIA%20bloc%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fall-is-well-bihar-ruling-alliance-denies-nitish-kumar-upset-india-rift-4727394%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22http