%20took%20office.%20It%20is%20during%20his%20term%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20awarded%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20site%20to%20a%20gaggle%20of%20individuals%20and%20groups%20linked%20politically%20to%20those%20who%20brought%20the%20mosque%20down%2C%20thereby%20legally%20endorsing%20what%20the%20vandals%20were%20demanding%20%E2%80%94%20and%20now%20the%20temple%20is%20ready%20to%20be%20inaugurated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20obvious%20therefore%20that%20Advani%20can%20be%20credited%20%E2%80%94%20if%20that%20is%20the%20word%20%E2%80%94%20for%20not%20just%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20rise%20but%20also%20the%20temple.%20To%20be%20not%20invited%20to%20its%20opening%20therefore%20must%20hurt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20that%20%E2%80%94%20Advani%20supported%20Modi%2C%20under%20whose%20rule%20Gujarat%20had%20seen%20brutal%20violence%20against%20Muslims%20in%202002%2C%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20BJP%20leadership%20wanted%20to%20remove%20him.%20And%20when%20Modi%20became%20PM%2C%20he%20did%20not%20acknowledge%20Advani%E2%80%99s%20debt.%20Advani%20and%20his%20senior%20colleagues%20were%20relegated%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98Margadarshak%20Mandal%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20bogus%20body%20of%20elders%20who%20would%20guide%20the%20party%2C%20which%20has%20never%20been%20heard%20of%20again.%20Putting%20them%20out%20to%20pasture%20meant%20that%20they%20have%20simply%20disappeared%20from%20public%20life.%20An%20entire%20generation%20has%20no%20clue%20who%20Advani%20or%20Joshi%20are.%20For%20them%2C%20Modi%20rises%20above%20everyone%20else%2C%20and%20he%20can%20do%20what%20he%20likes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20reading%20about%20the%20treatment%20meted%20out%20to%20the%20elders%20of%20BJP%20%E2%80%94%20in%20a%20society%20which%20is%20supposed%20to%20respect%20senior%20citizens%20%E2%80%94%20a%20question%20emerges%3A%20How%20should%20we%20react%20when%20Messrs%20Advani%20and%20Joshi%20are%20treated%20so%20disrespectfully%3F%20Should%20we%20feel%20bad%3F%20Should%20they%20have%20been%20invited%20to%20see%20the%20results%20of%20their%20hard%20work%3F%20Or%20is%20this%20just%20genuine%20concern%20about%20their%20age%20and%20health%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20journalists%20and%20others%20who%20have%20met%20Advani%20say%20he%20is%20extremely%20courteous%20and%20polite.%20Indeed%2C%20this%20is%20said%20of%20several%20BJP%20leaders%20of%20that%20era.%20Yet%2C%20somehow%2C%20it%20is%20very%20difficult%20to%20muster%20up%20any%20sympathy%20or%20righteous%20indignation%20at%20their%20plight.%20Anyone%20who%20was%20around%20at%20the%20time%20will%20recall%20India%20was%20riven%20by%20the%20Rath%20Yatra%20and%20what%20came%20after%2C%20how%20it%20brought%20out%20the%20ugliest%20in%20our%20society%2C%20and%20how%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20secular%20ethos%20was%20shattered%20in%20the%20worst%20possible%20way.%20That%20was%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20emergence%20of%20a%20virulent%20strain%20of%20communalism%2C%20which%20manifested%20itself%20not%20only%20as%20violence%20on%20the%20streets%2C%20but%20also%20showed%20up%20among%20urban%2C%20educated%20types%20who%20suddenly%20discovered%20their%20Hindu%20roots.%20In%20polite%20drawing%20rooms%2C%20urban%20sophisticates%20started%20talking%20about%20why%20Hindus%20needed%20to%20assert%20themselves%20in%20%E2%80%98their%20country%E2%80%99.%20Anti-minority%20sentiment%20was%20expressed%20freely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20virulent%20communalism%20seen%20in%20family%20WhatsApp%20groups%20now%20had%20its%20beginnings%20then.%20Twenty-five%20years%20after%20Advani%E2%80%99s%20cynical%20Rath%20Yatra%2C%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20and%20we%20have%20all%20seen%20what%20has%20happened%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20moment%2C%20watching%20what%20we%20have%20become%20and%20where%20we%20are%20heading%2C%20we%20may%20fall%20into%20the%20trap%20of%20thinking%20those%20were%20simpler%2C%20more%20innocent%20days.%20They%20were%20not.%20The%20Rath%20Yatra%20too%20was%20a%20grab%20for%20power%20using%20religion%2C%20but%20it%20succeeded%20only%20up%20to%20a%20point.%20The%20Vajpayee%20government%20was%20in%20a%20coalition%20where%20the%20partners%20acted%20as%20a%20brake%20to%20the%20more%20nefarious%20plans%20of%20the%20BJP%20(though%20even%20then%20there%20was%20interference%20in%20education%2C%20history%20and%20culture).%20The%20institutions%20held%20steadfast%20%E2%80%94%20the%20media%20was%20not%20so%20craven%2C%20the%20judiciary%20was%20independent%20and%20Parliament%20asked%20questions.%20And%20the%20Indian%20public%2C%20unconvinced%20by%20the%20tall%20claims%20of%20India%20Shining%2C%20threw%20out%20Vajpayee%20and%20his%20government%20in%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20we%20have%20no%20such%20respite%2C%20no%20checks%20and%20balances.%20Much%20of%20the%20media%20lies%20prostrate%2C%20the%20judiciary%20has%20decided%20to%20fall%20in%20place%2C%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20can%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20get%20their%20act%20together%2C%20and%20most%20frightening%20of%20all%2C%20the%20Indian%20public%20is%20in%20full%20Bhakti%20mode%2C%20supporting%20the%20government%20and%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20everything%2C%20even%20when%20its%20own%20interests%20are%20being%20hurt.%20All%20this%20is%20a%20result%20of%20that%20Rath%20Yatra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20an%20%E2%80%9Celder%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20progenitor%20of%20today%E2%80%99s%20India%2C%20is%20humiliated%20by%20his%20successors%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20feel%20bad%20for%20him.%20He%20is%20merely%20paying%20his%20dues.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703313055000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2Fmodi-advani-e1642151298688.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-ayodhya-ram-temple-and-lk-advanis-sour-grapes-of-rath%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20difficult%20to%20feel%20sympathy%20for%20the%20man%20whose%20yatra%20has%20led%20to%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20India%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3