C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20TMC%20MP%E2%80%99s%20excitable%20mimicry%20aimed%20at%20enthusing%20protesting%20opposition%20MPs%20has%20still%20been%20amplified%20by%20the%20BJP%20as%20an%20affront%20to%20not%20only%20the%20Jat%20community%20but%20also%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20chair.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuch%20double%20standards%20only%20remind%20one%20of%20a%20school%20bully%2C%20who%20takes%20pride%20in%20shaming%20and%20ragging%20weaker%20students%20but%20can%E2%80%99t%20take%20even%20the%20slightest%20blowback%20in%20good%20spirit.%20The%20suspended%20MPs%20were%20protesting%20outside%20when%20Banerjee%20stood%20up%20to%20enact%20his%20impression%20of%20Dhankhar.%20Between%20all%20the%20other%20important%20issues%20being%20raised%20by%20them%2C%20including%20demanding%20an%20official%20statement%20by%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20the%20Parliament%E2%80%99s%20security%20breach%2C%20and%20protesting%20against%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20high-handedness%2C%20mimicking%20Dhankhar%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20cheerful%20break%20for%20them.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20other%20MPs%20enjoyed%20the%20performance%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20also%20shot%20a%20video%20of%20it%20on%20his%20phone.%20But%20a%20majority%20of%20television%20channels%20went%20on%20an%20overdrive%20that%20Gandhi%20shot%20the%20video%20to%20circulate%20it%20with%20an%20intention%20to%20further%20heap%20insults%20on%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20chair.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmidst%20the%20spin-games%20by%20the%20ruling%20party%20to%20corner%20the%20opposition%2C%20the%20essential%20question%20that%20most%20have%20been%20asking%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20buried.%20Why%20has%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20not%20issued%20an%20official%20statement%20on%20the%20security%20breach%20in%20the%20Parliament%3F%20Both%20Shah%20and%20Modi%20have%20been%20giving%20interviews%20in%20the%20press%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20taken%20the%20security%20breach%20seriously%20and%20has%20ordered%20an%20inquiry.%20One%20also%20knows%20that%20the%20probe%20committee%20will%20be%20headed%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fitbp-dg-a-d-singh-given-additional-charge-of-crpf-9047016%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DITBP%2520Director%2520General%2520(DG)%2520Anish%2Can%2520official%2520order%2520said%2520Wednesday.%5C%22%3EAnish%20Dayal%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Director-General%20of%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20(CRPF)%2C%20the%20very%20agency%20that%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20security%20in%20the%20Parliament.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOpposition%20MPs%20have%20asked%20about%20a%20possible%20conflict%20of%20interest%20issue%20as%20it%20may%20not%20be%20right%2C%20at%20least%20in%20optics%2C%20for%20the%20CRPF%20Director-General%20to%20probe%20his%20own%20agency%E2%80%99s%20failure%20in%20the%20security%20breach.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%2C%20the%20government%20has%20chosen%20not%20to%20address%20any%20of%20these%20concerns.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20has%20not%20attended%20a%20single%20session%20of%20the%20Parliament%20in%20December.%20Shah%2C%20who%20tabled%20the%20amended%20Criminal%20Law%20Bills%20on%20Thursday%20(December%2021)%20and%20attempted%20to%20clear%20doubts%20on%20the%20new%20Bills%2C%20has%20evaded%20answering%20any%20of%20these%20serious%20questions%20in%20the%20Parliament.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOutside%20the%20House%2C%20parliamentary%20affairs%20minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20announced%20that%20the%20mimicry%20row%20shamed%20the%20entire%20country%20and%20blamed%20the%20opposition%20MPs%20for%20insulting%20the%20Jats%2C%20while%20also%20accusing%20them%20of%20shaming%20the%20Adivasis%20and%20Dalits%20when%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20and%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%20were%20chosen%20as%20the%20Presidents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20quite%20rightly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fcongress-rahul-gandhi-jantar-mantar-protest-mp-suspension-9078730%2F%5C%22%3Easked%3C%2Fa%3E%20whether%20he%20should%20also%20blame%20the%20ruling%20party%20MPs%20for%20not%20letting%20him%20speak%20in%20the%20House%20because%20he%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9CDalit%E2%80%9D.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20too%2C%20attacked%20the%20government%20for%20diverting%20attention%20from%20the%20questions%20that%20opposition%20MPs%20were%20raising%20and%20asked%20whether%20the%20TMC%20MP%E2%80%99s%20mimicry%20was%20more%20important%20than%20the%20concerns%20around%20security%20breach%20and%20unprecedented%20mass%20suspensions%20of%20opposition%20MPs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6MPs%20were%20sitting%20there%2C%20I%20shot%20their%20video.%20My%20video%20is%20on%20my%20phone.%20Media%20is%20showing%20it%E2%80%A6Nobody%20has%20said%20anything%E2%80%A6150%20of%20our%20MPs%20have%20been%20thrown%20out%20(of%20the%20House)%20but%20there%20is%20no%20discussion%20on%20that%20in%20the%20media.%20There%20is%20no%20discussion%20on%20Adani%2C%20no%20discussion%20on%20Rafale%2C%20no%20discussion%20on%20unemployment.%20Our%20MPs%20are%20disheartened%20and%20sitting%20outside.%20But%20you%20are%20discussing%20that%20(mimicry)%E2%80%A6%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gandhi%20asked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmidst%20the%20suspensions%2C%20controversial%20new%20laws%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftelecom-bill-2023-is-a-repackaged-version-of-the-archaic-colonial-law%5C%22%3ETelecommunications%20Bill%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwatershed-moment-says-modi-as-rajya-sabha-passes-three-criminal-bills-in-absence-of-opposition%5C%22%3ECriminal%20Law%20Bills%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20passed%20without%20any%20discussion%2C%20even%20as%20the%20BJP%20amplified%20the%20mimicry%20row%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20pliant%20media%20and%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20even%20the%20Speaker%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20chair%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20as%20the%20mimicry%20row%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20an%20affront%20by%20Dhankhar%20and%20his%20Jat%20identity%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20subverted%20the%20democratic%20functioning%20of%20the%20Parliament%20by%20bulldozing%20through%20parliamentary%20rules%20through%20its%20brute%20majority.%20It%20used%20its%20majority%20to%20put%20into%20effect%20the%20largest%20suspensions%20of%20MPs%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Indian%20Parliament%2C%20and%20simultaneously%20evade%20accountability%20on%20the%20matter%20of%20security%20breach%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%2C%20when%20the%20opposition%20MPs%20attempted%20to%20subvert%20such%20autocracy%20through%20a%20humorous%20take%20by%20an%20MP%2C%20it%20has%20become%20the%20biggest%20talking%20point%20in%20India.%20Such%20misplaced%20priorities%20not%20only%20reflect%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20but%20also%20the%20media%20which%20has%20unquestioningly%20fallen%20in%20line%2C%20even%20if%20it%20meant%20a%20steep%20fall%20in%20our%20parliamentary%20tradition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20this%20regime%2C%20stand-up%20comics%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmunawar-faruqui-arrest-indian-american-stand-up-comics-freedom-of-speech%5C%22%3Ehave%20been%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdelhi-police-denies-permission-to-munawar-faruquis-show-after-pressure-from-hindu-right%5C%22%3Earrested%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20their%20shows%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Ffir-comedians-vir-das-kunal-kamra-munawar-faruqui-tanmay-b