er%20time%20in%20the%20prices%20paid%20by%20rural%20labourers%20for%20a%20basket%20of%20goods%20and%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CPI-AL%20in%20November%20this%20year%20increased%2012%20points%20to%201%2C253%2C%20while%20the%20index%20for%20rural%20workers%20advanced%2011%20points%20to%201%2C262%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20indices%20were%201%2C241%20points%20and%201%2C251%20points%2C%20respectively%2C%20in%20October%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20was%20driven%20by%20an%20increase%20in%20prices%20of%20rice%2C%20wheat%20atta%2C%20pulses%2C%20onion%2C%20turmeric%20whole%2C%20garlic%2C%20mixed%20spices%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20noted%20that%20there%20has%20been%20an%20upward%20trend%20in%20the%20index%20across%20all%20the%20states%20except%20West%20Bengal%20(both%20CPI-AL%20and%20CPI-RL%20indices%20decreased)%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20(CPI-AL%20index%20decreased).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703253254000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F01175204%2Fagriculture.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Frising-food-prices-push-november-retail-inflation-to-7-37-for-farm-workers-7-for-rural-labourers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20figures%20were%20higher%20than%20October's%20rates%20of%207.08%25%20and%206.92%25%20for%20farm%20workers%20and%20rural%20labourers%2C%20respectively.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Frising-food-prices-push-november-retail-inflation-to-7-37-for-farm-workers-7-for-rural-labourers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pornhub%20fined%20over%20'sex%20trafficked'%20videos%20scandal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703252580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F70x70%2Fskynews-pornhub-mindgeek_6401546.jpg%3F20231222140718%22%2C%22o