at%20too%20exported%2C%20so%20there%20were%20not%20many%20patients%20that%20could%20afford%20to%20pay%20those%20two%20to%20three%20lakh%20rupees%20more%20for%20robotic%20surgery.%20It%20was%20around%20this%20time%20when%20I%20met%20the%2022-year-old%20patient%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20incident%20made%20the%20doctor%20realise%20that%20the%20country%20needs%20a%20system%20that%20is%20cheaper.%20%E2%80%9CBecause%20of%20the%20high%20costs%20we%20cannot%20offer%20the%20best%20treatment%20to%20the%20patients%2C%20and%20to%20reduce%20the%20cost%2C%20we%20have%20to%20develop%20it%20in%20the%20country%20itself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20doctor%20made%20a%20commitment%20to%20the%20cause%20and%20decided%20to%20put%20his%20practice%20on%20hold%20in%202013.%20%E2%80%9CHaving%20done%20over%201%2C400%20surgeries%20and%20with%20my%20knowledge%20of%20robotic%20surgeries%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20use%20my%20life%20savings%20of%204.5%20million%20dollars%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20I%20went%20to%20Germany%20to%20meet%20some%20of%20their%20scientists%20for%20an%20exchange%20of%20technology.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20not%20a%20success.%20Then%2C%20I%20came%20back%20to%20India%20and%20formed%20a%20team%20of%2010%20engineers%20and%20started%20the%20development%20out%20of%20my%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20robotic%20surgeries%20and%20how%20do%20they%20work%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Sudhir%20explains%20why%20robotic%20surgeries%20are%20important.%20%E2%80%9CDepth%2C%20precision%20and%20safety.%20These%20are%20three%20things%20that%20surmise%20why%20we%20need%20robotic%20surgeries.%20With%20the%20help%20of%20technology%2C%20the%20surgeon%20gets%20an%20in-depth%20picture%20of%20the%20patient%E2%80%99s%20parts%20to%20be%20operated%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-i